column5: Flying in in mid August, seen solos report, looked great for eating walleye. Any hot spots anyone can share, or points to concentrate on? Any decent pike in there? Any and all comments welcome, can't wait.
Bump, has anyone fished Abbey with Parks?
Sent you a pm with some info but if you've read Mike's report you've got all you'll need for a trip to Abbey. Beautiful little lake that I'll be heading back to one day.
